---
---

<section id="process">
  <div class="inner">

    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="stag">How It Works</div>
      <h2>From First Call to<br />Final Handover</h2>
      <p class="sdesc">A clear, structured process so you always know exactly where your project stands.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">

      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3-8.59A2 2 0 0 1 3.61 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 9.4a16 16 0 0 0 6.29 6.29l.95-.96a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Free Consultation</h3>
          <p>We discuss your vision, requirements, and budget. A site visit is arranged to assess your space and understand exactly what you want.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3a2.85 2.83 0 1 1 4 4L7.5 20.5 2 22l1.5-5.5L17 3z"/><path d="M15 5l4 4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Design & Planning</h3>
          <p>Our team produces a 3D design and civil plan tailored to your bathroom. You review, refine, and approve before any work begins.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Material Selection</h3>
          <p>Choose your tiles, fixtures, and finishes from our curated selection or your own supplier. We guide every decision to ensure quality and coherence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="16"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="14" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Construction & Renovation</h3>
          <p>Our skilled team executes the full renovation — waterproofing, tiling, flooring, staircase details, plumbing, electrical and finishing work — with weekly photo updates sent to you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">05</div>
        <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M21 12c-1 0-3-1-3-3V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4c0 2-2 3-3 3s3 1 3 3v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4c0-2 2-3 3-3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Final Quality Inspection</h3>
          <p>A thorough inspection covers every surface, fitting, and finish. Any snagging items are resolved before we consider the project complete.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">06</div>
        <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h3>Project Handover</h3>
          <p>Your completed space is handed over clean, detailed, and ready to use. Full documentation and care guidance is provided at handover.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="process-cta reveal">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Start Your Free Consultation</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 5.5rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-head {
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .stag {
    font-size: .72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--clay);
    margin-bottom: .75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: .9rem;
  }

  .sdesc {
    font-size: .95rem;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  /* ── Steps ── */

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step {
    padding: 2.2rem 2rem 2.2rem 0;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--stone);
    padding-right: 2rem;
    padding-left: 0;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .step:nth-child(3n) {
    border-right: none;
    padding-right: 0;
  }

  .step:nth-child(n+4) {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--stone);
    padding-top: 2.2rem;
  }

  .step:not(:nth-child(3n)) {
    padding-left: 0;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .step:nth-child(3n+2),
  .step:nth-child(3n) {
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .step-line { display: none; }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(184,148,90,.18);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -.04em;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 2.8rem;
    height: 2.8rem;
    background: rgba(184,148,90,.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,148,90,.22);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--clay);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  p {
    font-size: .84rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--warm-gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */

  .process-cta {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: .85rem 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: .8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    min-height: 48px;
    transition: background .2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--clay); }

  /* ── Responsive ── */

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    section { padding-left: 2.5rem; padding-right: 2.5rem; }
    .steps { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .step:nth-child(3n) {
      border-right: 1px solid var(--stone);
    }
    .step:nth-child(2n) {
      border-right: none;
    }
    .step:nth-child(n+4) {
      border-top: none;
    }
    .step:nth-child(n+3) {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--stone);
    }
    .step:nth-child(3n+2),
    .step:nth-child(3n) {
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }
    .step:nth-child(2n) {
      padding-right: 0;
    }
    .step:nth-child(2n+1) {
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .step {
      border-right: none !important;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--stone) !important;
      padding: 1.8rem 0 !important;
    }
    .step:first-child { border-top: none !important; padding-top: 0 !important; }
  }
</style>
